{"data":{"items":[{"content":"{\"images\":[],\"audios\":[],\"imageTotalCount\":0,\"audioTotalCount\":0,\"text\":\"虽然你在认真修改，但你的内心是纠结的。把心调整到与行为合一的状态。尊重【字形需要多次修改才能写像】的这个客观事实，不要逃避这个学习过程。\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2022-11-08T21:59:36+0800","evaluateStatus":1,"id":11962593,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20220511/2022051101011927165296.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户3731vgdwn","identity":2,"nickName":"一定写好字吖","userId":157254108},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"images\":[],\"audios\":[],\"imageTotalCount\":0,\"audioTotalCount\":0,\"text\":\"一种是屏气凝神的追求结构，一种是气定神闲的让线条自然舒展开来构成字形。 两种状态是不一样的。 不追求，不冒进，这样的心态才能更好完成目标。 追求反而求而不得。\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2022-11-08T21:47:24+0800","evaluateStatus":1,"id":11962481,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20220511/2022051101011927165296.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户3731vgdwn","identity":2,"nickName":"一定写好字吖","userId":157254108},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"images\":[],\"audios\":[],\"imageTotalCount\":0,\"audioTotalCount\":0,\"text\":\"不要追求【把结构写像，所以憋着气写完一根根线条】，把注意力放在【放松踏实缓慢地高质量完成每一根线条，慢下来，放松下来，笔锋就自然落下去了，线条踏实了，然后形状不是一两次就写成，是多次的修改而后自然变好】  字形必然是多次的修正，才能变好。你如果想几次就写很像，那才是不尊重客观规律。 \",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2022-11-08T21:41:59+0800","evaluateStatus":1,"id":11962459,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20220511/2022051101011927165296.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户3731vgdwn","identity":2,"nickName":"一定写好字吖","userId":157254108},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"images\":[],\"audios\":[],\"imageTotalCount\":0,\"audioTotalCount\":0,\"text\":\"不彻底把笔锋铺下去，力量端着不落地，你呼吸都不顺畅。 练习是有次第顺序的。现在线条的质量是第一位。粗壮一点没什么不好。\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2022-11-08T21:35:06+0800","evaluateStatus":1,"id":11962434,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20220511/2022051101011927165296.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户3731vgdwn","identity":2,"nickName":"一定写好字吖","userId":157254108},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"images\":[],\"audios\":[],\"imageTotalCount\":0,\"audioTotalCount\":0,\"text\":\"放心笔锋铺下去，感觉为了线条细而端着了，力道不落地，丧失了中锋的质量就是本末倒置了。\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2022-11-08T21:32:48+0800","evaluateStatus":1,"id":11962373,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20220511/2022051101011927165296.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户3731vgdwn","identity":2,"nickName":"一定写好字吖","userId":157254108},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"醍醐灌顶\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2022-11-09T07:45:06+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":11963914,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20220602/2022060211011010311044.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户8305iudbw","identity":0,"nickName":"今天航海【0069】","userId":157711978},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"感觉这线条不干净，毛毛躁躁的。\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2022-11-08T20:53:41+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":11962187,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20231024/2023102401502466126073.jpg","ccUserName":"而归儿","identity":2,"nickName":"而归【0087】","userId":158130835},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"今天这状态明显没昨天好\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2022-11-08T20:48:54+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":11962167,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20231024/2023102401502466126073.jpg","ccUserName":"而归儿","identity":2,"nickName":"而归【0087】","userId":158130835},"userPower":0}],"nextPage":false},"message":"success","status":0}